{"tid":1828870,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"用機場熒幕打 PS4   美國男子即被機場保安制止","createTime":"2020-01-18T08:43:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-18T09:11:12.000Z","uid":28114,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"83d5522c095235ebc866f732924de4bb333288a7","tid":1828870,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T08:43:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/thumbnail.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2Fthumbnail.jpeg&h=acaeff1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n搭飛機有時遇上 delay 在機場上無限等待，往往令人悶到發荒。不少朋友會拿出手機看 YouTube、打機或者滑FB，但美國就有一名男子把自己帶來的 PS4 駁到機場的熒幕上開戰。<br />\n<br />\n在美國波特蘭國際機場有一名男子被發現把自己帶來的 PS4 遊戲機，連接到機場播放資訊的一個熒幕上，並玩起了《Apex Legends》來。根據當地電台 KXL 報道，男子打機不久後即有機場營運經理到場了解情況，據了解經理很友善地要求該男子馬上收拾起他的遊戲機，這名男子亦很有禮貌地詢問能否完成那場戰鬥，不過最後也被拒絕了。<br />\n<br />\n這個熒幕是展示機場內部資訊，並非航班資訊，看起上來也不會影響其他人。不過當時職員還是要求該男子盡早收拾機器。發言人表示：「這顯然是我們不希望會發生的事情，其他旅客需要透過我們的熒幕獲得他們所需的訊息。」<br />\n<br />\n還好報道中這名男子連接的是一部遊戲機，如果有人把奇怪的裝置，插上機場設施，恐怕下場不是這樣了。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/01/18/airportps4/fun-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F01%2F18%2Fairportps4%2Ffun-tech%2F&d=qHKTGL1WilUkyN31MLoEKJMONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=842f4a3d\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/01/18/airportps4/fun-tech/</a>"},{"pid":"15dc9994da31c0fdfd581016454668e7765e52a6","tid":1828870,"uid":124400,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T08:45:40.000Z","msg":"據了解經理很友善地要求該男子馬上收拾起他的遊戲機，這名男子亦很有禮貌地詢問能否完成那場戰鬥，不過最後也被拒絕了。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e01c34b502149bbde001ca0f89b8b9df6d5a3d59","tid":1828870,"uid":55511,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T08:47:00.000Z","msg":"打埋呢場"},{"pid":"cf99a6f256762bb3495ee0706810f2754d60baf3","tid":1828870,"uid":42655,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T08:47:17.000Z","msg":"唔走場 遊戲家精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a904d92248e1b2f689be009cc2364f11d09290c9","tid":1828870,"uid":18196,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"e01c34b502149bbde001ca0f89b8b9df6d5a3d59","tid":1828870,"uid":55511,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T08:47:00.000Z","msg":"打埋呢場"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T08:48:25.000Z","msg":"好快好快 等陣"},{"pid":"cd79c92444483334aa0769b97a46d0f6f2b5c027","tid":1828870,"uid":66365,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T08:48:38.000Z","msg":"一場又一場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af1612a5892ed6d631a1dd379d5579b090325b57","tid":1828870,"uid":8014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T08:51:05.000Z","msg":"中離會比隊友屌 經理體諒下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c43e3ab7f1527ea533ab862b30e48485d6e4c5b","tid":1828870,"uid":218407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T08:54:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":